snippet.title: ABYSS BOAT - PC Full Playthrough (アビスボート)
snippet.description:
Full walkthrough of the Japanese game Abyss Boat for windows.
This was a free game that was sent to members of the Leaf fan club.

I had to record this game using my Windows XP machine (not virtual) so the video quality isn't the best.

Developed by Aquaplus (アクアプラス) 2002.
